Dialogue: 4,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, urobil som to pre vás.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurá!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohňostroj, ohňostroj!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urobíme ho, urobíme ho!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:37.98,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem vám dať strelný prach, ale môžem vám dať nejaké diely?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:43.32,0:10:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasné!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, dokázali sme to!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujeme vám, pane!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujeme vám!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:04.93,0:11:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, tak to urobíme z bambusu?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:09.12,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím si, že červená farba by vyzerala roztomilo.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:13.51,0:11:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roztomilo?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty sa naozaj odlišuješ od toho ako vyzeráš...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže svetlo bude tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo bude tu?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to je len dekorácia.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uľahčuje to preniesť na odpálenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toto je to isté.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.31,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Skvelé, skvelé!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:32.31,0:11:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je skvelé!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, vieš čo!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, nepúšťaj to!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo, už si skončil?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve ti skočila na chrbát.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:49.76,0:11:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma-san, pusti ma.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppopopo!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:00.84,0:12:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem ju vidieť, ale vidím ju.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ju vidím.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem vyhrať.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:11.60,0:12:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemohla som vyhrať vtedy a nemôžem vyhrať ani teraz.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem kúpiť nejakú limonádu.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zachránila si ma.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Že si utiekla.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som, že začnem kričať.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:52.28,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem, že Menma je s nami.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:56.06,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nemôžeme ju vidieť.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôže ani hovoriť.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:02.75,0:13:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem ju stretnúť zase.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, prečo je Yadomi jediný, ktorý...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musí to byť Yadomi.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:10.72,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pre Yadomiho musí byť Menma.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odvtedy sa nič nezmenilo.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už si to vzdala?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:19.26,0:13:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Začala si ho volať Jin-tan, ale zase ho voláš Yadomi.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:23.81,0:13:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo rozprávaš, ako keby si cez mňa videl?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidím len cez teba.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal by som, že je to súdržnosť medzi dvomi rovnakými ľuďmi.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem byť rovnaký blbec ako si ty!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, upokoj sa...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:11.47,0:14:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To, čo som predtým povedal...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:13.13,0:14:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslel som to vážne.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Predtým?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Žeby sme išli spolu niekam.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si beznádejná, pokiaľ ide o chlapcov.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robíš si srandu?!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekný kop.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si neuveriteľný!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíš tým "pekný kop"?!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň sa mi smiať!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj si ma prekvapil!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolo to prekvapivé, však?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V tento deň.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To začína!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:48.79,0:14:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Jin-tan.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru tu nie je.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru už išla domov?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, naozaj sa ponáhľala.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je naozaj ako malé mačiatko.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:02.29,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak splníš Menme jej prianie, nebude ti vadiť, keď potom zmizne?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deje sa niečo, Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nič...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja práca sa začína skoro.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš už?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:18.49,0:15:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma a čo ty?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem s Poppo.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona chce zostať tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:23.71,0:15:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to v poriadku?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chápem...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samozrejme, že môžeš!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj sa tu cíť ako doma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:32.21,0:15:34.57,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurá! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beháš príliš veľa.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lebo som šťastná!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si šťastná, však Menma?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:43.37,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.54,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, videl som to.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:49.54,0:15:52.07,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde jeden stredoškolák bojuje s nunčakmi.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zimná uniforma...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.80,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečne si to videl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakoniec...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som si myslel, že bola letná beštia.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.49,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kúpil som si už DVD.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, majú už na sebe zimné uniformy.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.02,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že bude pokračovanie.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:03.02,0:16:03.81,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pokračovanie?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:03.81,0:16:08.12,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dievča s nunčakmi, ktorá bojuje v Hong Kongu so zombie?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, napísala som to!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, si tu?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, som!
