Dialogue: 4,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrime sa...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V ten deň...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela si...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vieš, že vtedy...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja...
Dialogue: 4,0:16:58.77,0:17:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, poďme sa hrať na reťazovú poštu!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S obrázkami.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, čo to je?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:08.94,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyzerá to ako koláč.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Batoh...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marble...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:17.48,0:17:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruky!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:20.21,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatlieskajte rukami a budete mať šťastie!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďalekohľad!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma začína vyšetrovať ako detektív!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som doma.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:09.49,0:18:14.74,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Číslo, ktoré voláte je momentálne nedostupné.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra, nemôžem sa mu dovolať.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo chodím tak rýchlo?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo utekám?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma bude pravdepodobne v tajnej skrýši.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Napriek tomu, prečo...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, tu som!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma-chan, ona...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem, aby Menma odišla!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:11.86,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:35.28,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem, aby si zomrel! Nikdy!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to s tebou?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si už mŕtva.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si divná, Menma.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si ten, kto je divný!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, bola tam ryba Koi.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koi?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol tam jeden naozaj veľký.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcela som ho vidieť z blízka.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidíš, tam je!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blízko koreňa stromu.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:13.55,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plával okolo.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolí, Jin-tan.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, chceš sa túliť?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navždy...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostaň tu navždy...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostaň... Ostaň tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja pôjdem po rybu Koi.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, budeš mokrý!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hlúpy Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prechladneš!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.72,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Naše leto sa skončilo.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.72,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Kimi to natsu no owari
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.72,0:21:32.43,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Nezabudnem na veľké nádeje a sny o budúcnosti.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.72,0:21:32.43,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Shourai no yume ooki na kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.43,0:21:39.08,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Verím, že sa zase stretneme o desať rokov v auguste ako teraz.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.43,0:21:39.08,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Juunengo no hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.64,0:21:47.63,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\be6}Ďakujem ti za spomienky.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.64,0:21:47.63,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\be6}Saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.55,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Náhodou sme sa stretli v tomto momente.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.55,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Deai wa futto shita shunkan
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.74,0:21:56.27,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Na križovatke na mojej ceste domov.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.74,0:21:56.27,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Kaerimichi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.27,0:22:01.87,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Povedal si mi: "Poďme domov spolu".
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.27,0:22:01.87,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Koe wo kakete kureta ne "issho ni kaerou"
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.04,0:22:06.63,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Bola som tak šťastná a všetko bolo také zábavné.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.04,0:22:06.63,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Ureshikutte tanoshikutte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.63,0:22:10.22,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Zažili sme spolu veľa dobrodružstiev.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:06.63,0:22:10.22,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Bouken mo iroiro shita ne
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.22,0:22:17.33,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Vo vnútri v našej tajnej skrýši.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:17.33,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Futari no himitsu no kichi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.58,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Naše leto sa skončilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.58,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Kimi to natsu no owari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:24.52,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Nezabudnem na veľké nádeje a sny o budúcnosti.
