Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:35.71,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Viem, že si mi povedal "ďakujem"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:35.71,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)\be6}Kimi ga saigo made kokoro kara "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:38.87,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}S tvojím srdcom až do samého konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:38.87,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,180)\be6}Sakendeita koto shitteita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:45.96,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Bolo to tak veľmi ťažké udržať slzy a rozlúčiť sa s úsmevom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:45.96,Ending-jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,180)\be6}Namida wo koraete egao de sayounara setsunai yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:54.15,Ending-sk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,1080)\be6}Ďakujem ti za spomienky.
